            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Α Ω <lb n="2"/>ex antiquis renovatum est per Paternum <expan><abbr>reverentiss</abbr><ex>imum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>episc</abbr><ex>opum</ex></expan> nostrum amen </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ἔχει καθαρ<supplied reason="lost">οῦ ἀργυρίου</supplied> λίτρας κʹ οὐγκίας ηʹ γράμματα ιϛʹ καὶ <supplied reason="lost">καθαροῦ</supplied> χρυ<supplied reason="lost">σίου</supplied> οὐγκίας βʹ γράμματα κʹ καὶ μι<supplied reason="lost">κτοῦ</supplied> χρυσ<supplied reason="lost">ίου</supplied> νο<supplied reason="lost">μίσματα</supplied> βʹ </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ominus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>oster</ex></expan> Anastasius <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Μηννᾶ </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ἰωάννου κόμητ&amp;lt;ο=Α&amp;gt;ς </ab></div><div n="6" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ἀν(αστάσιος)<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> Ξενοφίλου 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Lateinische Inschrift auf der Innenseite eines silbernen Tellers. Griechische Inschrift auf der unteren Seite.</p>
            </div>
